exports.getModelData = function (callback) {
    callback({
        alert: 'info',
        dismissible: true,
        caption: 'Not yet implemented',
        footer: 'Please check back later',
        'alert-classes': 'feature-tbd-alert',
        'activate-on': 'click'
    });
}
